136 10. Any rule or portion of a rule, as that term is defined in section 536.010, that is
137 created under the authority delegated in this section shall become effective only if it complies
138 with and is subject to all of the provisions of chapter 536 and, if applicable, section 536.028.
139 This section and chapter 536 are nonseverable and if any of the powers vested with the
